org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id INNER JOIN member_roles ON member_roles.member_id = members.id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND member_roles.role_id IN ("$3", "$4") LIMIT "$5"
